<title>Eye On Medicine/Bulletin/Full Story/Turkey Roasting Times -- Newer
Information 10/29/96</title>
<meta name="CreatedBy" content="WP Internet Publisher 6.1">
</head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFF4C8">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/images/glassesicon.gif" border =0 ALT="glassesicon">
</CENTER>   
<P>
<CENTER>

<B><H1>WELCOME TO THE EYE ON MEDICINE BULLETIN</H1></B><H3>October 29, 1996</H3><HR>




<a href="/money/mon1.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/x064300a.gif"></a><P>
