<TITLE>Eye On Medicine/Bulletin/Full Story/Chronic Pain Insomnia/8-3-96 </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFF4C8">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="/images/glassesicon.gif" border =0 ALT="glassesicon">
</CENTER>   
<P>
<CENTER>

<B><H1>WELCOME TO THE EYE ON MEDICINE BULLETIN</H1></B><H3>August 6, 1996</H3><HR>




<a href="/money/mon1.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/x064300a.gif"></a><P>
<!-- BEGIN INTERNET LINK EXCHANGE CODE -->
<a href="http://ad.linkexchange.com/43/X064300/gotoad.map" 
