<HEAD>
<TITLE>Eye On Medicine/Bulletin/Full Story/Wife Abuse 9/20/96 </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFF4C8">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="PMEAL.BMP" border =0 ALT="glassesicon">
</CENTER>   
<P>
<CENTER>

<B><H1>WELCOME TO THE EYE ON MEDICINE WEEKLY BULLETIN</H1></B><H3>September 20, 1996</H3><HR>




<a href="/money/mon1.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/x064300a.gif"></a><P>
<!-- BEGIN INTERNET LINK EXCHANGE CODE -->
<a href="http://ad.linkexchange.com/45/X064300/gotoad.map" 
