<HEAD>
<TITLE>Court TV Casefiles: O.J. Simpson Transcripts</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#DD0000">
<A HREF="/map/top-casefiles.map"><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/headers/top-casefiles.gif" ISMAP BORDER=0></A>
<BR CLEAR=ALL>

<H2>The O.J. Simpson Civil Trial Transcripts</H2>

<P>NOTE: Some of these files are quite long (200k+) and may take a few minutes to load. If you prefer, you may download a compressed (zipped) version of the file to your hard drive. (You'll need an <A HREF="/download/utility/">unzipping utility</A> to decompress the file).</P>

<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT>

<H4><A HREF="excerpt.html">Read excerpts</A> from the three-day direct examination of O.J. Simpson.</H4>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec20.html"><B>Friday, December 20</B></A><BR>
Testimony from defense expert witnesses on photography and forensic toxicology.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Robert Groden, Frederic Rieders</I></P>

<P><B>Thursday, December 19</B><BR>
No Transcript; Court not in session.</P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec18.html"><B>Wednesday, December 18</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec18.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Testimony from defense expert witness on photography.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Daniel Gonzalez, Robert Groden</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec17.html"><B>Tuesday, December 17</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec17.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Further testimony from defense pathologist, as well as additional witnesses from the LAPD.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Michael Baden, William Blasini (Testimony read), Gilbert Aguilar, Michael Gladden, Thomas Tallarino, Daniel Gonzalez</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec16.html"><B>Monday, December 16</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec16.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Testimony from the defense forensics experts.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Herbert MacDonell, Michael Baden</I></P>

<P><B>Friday, December 13</B><BR>
No Transcript; Court not in session.</P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec12.html"><B>Thursday, December 12</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec12.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
Testimony from the DNA expert for the defense.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Kelly Mulldorfer, Frank Spangler, John Gerdes</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec11.html"><B>Wednesday, December 11</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec11.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
The defense recalled police witnesses as part of their case.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Tom Lange, Susan Brockbank, Stephen Valerie, Willie Ford, Wayne Stanfield, Howard Bingham</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec10.html"><B>Tuesday, December 10</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec10.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
The first full day of the defense.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Philip Vanatter, Andrea Mazzola, Thano Peratis, Gregory Matheson, Tom Lange</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec09.html"><B>Monday, December 9</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec09.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
The final day of the plaintiffs' case. Includes testimony from the father of victim Ron Goldman.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Fred Goldman, Philip Vanatter</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec06.html"><B>Friday, December 6</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec06.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
The plaintiffs begin to wrap up their case. Includes testimony from the mothers of the victims.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Bruce Weir, Leroy Taft, Robert Kardashian (Deposition), Sharon Rufo (Deposition), Juditha Brown (Deposition)</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec05.html"><B>Thursday, December 5</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec05.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
More witnesses called by the plaintiffs to refute the testimony of O.J. Simpson.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Randall Petee, Dr. Leonore E. A. Walker (Deposition), Jim Merrill (Deposition), Mark Partridge (Deposition)</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec04.html"><B>Wednesday, December 4</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec04.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
More witnesses called by the plaintiffs to refute the testimony of O.J. Simpson, including videotaped testimony from his former girlfriend.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> Nancy Ney, Ron Fischman, Paula Barbieri (Deposition), Leslie Gardner, Josephine Guarin, Dale St. John, Randall Petee</I></P>

<P><A HREF="dec/dec03.html"><B>Tuesday, December 3</B></A><BR>
<I><A HREF="dec/dec03.zip">Download a zipped version</A></I><BR>
The plaintiffs called a number of witnesses to refute the testimony of O.J. Simpson.<BR>
<I><B>Witnesses:</B> India Allen, Albert Aguilera, Charles Cale, Allen Cowlings, Jackie Cooper, Donna Estes, Craig Baumgarten</I></P>

<P><B>Monday, December 2</B><BR>
No Transcript; Court not in session.</P>

<P><A HREF="nov/"><B>Transcripts from November</B></A></P>

<P><A HREF="oct/"><B>Transcripts from October</B></A></P>

<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT>

<P><A HREF="http://www.courttv.com/gateway.html"><B>Talk Back!</B></A><BR>
What do you think will happen in the civil suit against O.J. Simpson? What's the best part of these transcripts? Talk to other Simpson-watchers in our <A HREF=/discuss/gateway.html>discussion group</a>.</P>

