<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>President Clinton or President Dole?</H1>
<p>
Who do you think should take the election in November? Register your opinion here with our new Opinion Meter. 
The further to the side you move the slider, the more strongly you feel. 
(For example, if you think you'd vote for
Bob Dole but aren't too enthusiastic about him, you might move the slider
to the right about 30 percent.) When you're finished, enter your e-mail
address in the box below and click on the Submit button.
