<H2>Simpson Civil Case: Key Witnesses</H2>

<P><B>(Selections from the <A HREF="witness.html">full witness
list</A>)</B></P>

<P><FONT SIZE="+1"><B>Key Witnesses for Plaintiffs</B></FONT><BR>
<B>Jennifer Ameli -- </B>A psychotherapist who said she treated Nicole Brown
Simpson<BR>
<B>Paula Barbieri (video) -- </B>former girlfriend of O.J. Simpson<BR>
<B>William Bodziak -- </B>FBI special agent<BR>
<B>Susan Brockbank -- </B>LAPD criminalist<BR>
