        16            Q.    Yeah?

        17            A.    Certainly not.

        18            Q.    And, in fact, the results that Roger

        19     Martz got from both the socks and the blood on the

        20     back gate were just about the same, weren't they?

        21            A.    No, if you look at the chromatogram, they

        22     differ.

