A. No. An employee, a company worker called me and said that the
police received a tip that Danny DeVito's driver witnessed something
on that night and she said that I needed to go in and talk to them.

Q. Were you Danny DeVito's driver?

A. I work for Jersey Films, and yes, I drove him at times.

