MR. LAMBERT: Beyond the scope, Your Honor.

THE COURT: Overruled.

A. Yes. I'm aware of that testimony.

Q. (BY MR. BLASIER) And you're aware that her initials don't show up
on any of those bindles?

A. That's correct.

Q. And you're aware that she testified that according to the procedure
used by the LAPD lab, the swatches that went into the bindles were dry
