opening statement, we would request that

you immediately designate those portions

of Dr. Lee's testimony you intend to

offer into evidence."

Going on to explain, this is in light of your -- The Court's ruling
September 23.

No response to that letter was received.

On December 1, 1996, I wrote a letter to Mr. Baker, indicating that we
had still not received the designation of the portions of the
