Q. August 4, 1994.

A. Take me just a minute to find it in my notes.

Yes, it was August 4.

(Witness reviews notes.)

Q. That was the first time, to your knowledge, that the socks were
examined for any fiber evidence; is that correct?

A. That was the only time I examined them for fiber evidence.

Q. And when they were given to you, both socks were contained in one
