A. Yes. That was June 19, '95.

Q. Isn't it accurate that -- well, withdrawn.

You also measured a pair of new Aris leather lights, extra large,
produced by the prosecution in the criminal case, correct?

A. Yes, I did.

Q. And it's accurate, is it not, that the size of the Rockingham and
