A. Yes.

Q. To your knowledge?

A. Yes.

Q. Now, when you cut a piece of carpet, isn't it true that the carpet
fibers get very fragile along the edges, in the sense that you're
likely to get stuff falling off of that if you're not careful?

A. Yes. You usually get some yarns falling off.

Q. Okay.

And the carpet fibers that you had examined, or found, on other pieces
