A. No.

Q. Okay.

That the grand jury -- do you recall being asked the following
questions and giving the following answers:

I'm referring to page 370, line 23. Start at line 26.

Do you recall being asked this question at the grand jury: "Q. Can you
describe for us

what is the method by which you removed

